sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as Citizen / Party
    participant App as Khural dApp
    participant ENC as Encrypted Contract (Civil Layer)
    participant J as Judge (Judicial DAO)
    participant JONFT as Judicial Order NFT
    participant ACL as Access Control (ZK/Policy)
    participant AUD as Audit Log

    U->>App: Report fraud / request access
    App->>J: Case submission (evidence, hashes)
    J->>JONFT: Issue time-bound order (scope, purpose)
    JONFT-->>ACL: Register order (who/what/why, expiry)
    App->>ACL: Request decrypt (least privilege)
    ACL->>ACL: Verify SeatSBT + JONFT validity
    ACL->>ENC: Partial decrypt (scoped fields only)
    ENC-->>App: Encrypted payload slice
    App-->>U: Revealed fields (minimal necessary)
    ACL-->>AUD: Append access event (who/what/why/when)
    Note over J,JONFT: Judge may revoke order early\nor let it auto-expire